content:
Nominations & Appointments

October 26, 2020
NOMINATION SENT TO THE SENATE:Stephen Andrew Kubiatowski, of Kentucky, to be a Judge of the United States Court of Federal Claims for a term of fifteen years, vice Margaret Mary Sweeney, term expired.WITHDRAWAL SENT TO THE SENATE:Stephen Andrew Kubiatowski, of Kentucky, to be a Judge of the United States Court of Federal Claims for a term of fifteen years, vice Thomas Craig Wheeler, term expiring, which was sent to the Senate on October 23, 2020.
